Steps to display or remove items from the header of every object in lightning components.

1.Click on the setup and then click on the object manager 
2. Select the object you want for example select (Account) then click on Compact layout
3.click on the System default compact loyout.
4.then click on Clone button at the top and give the name of your layout and select the fields you want then click save.\
5.Now click on the layout you created and then click on Compact layout assignment
6.Click on the edit assignment and select the layout you created from the dropdown button the click save
7.You have successfully added the fields now refresh you tab to see the changes. 

